originalText.text: I am so grateful for the amazing care Dr. Moritz has provided.  When I developed some unusual complications during my last pregnancy, he was able to guide me through the rest of my pregnancy and delivery safely.  I ended up needing a c-section, which caused me a great deal of anxiety.  Dr. Moritz was respectful of my anxiety and talked me through the whole process.  He is also an extremely skilled surgeon.  I honestly don’t know what we would have done without him.  Dr. Moritz is not only knowledgeable but also accessible.  When I had questions during my pregnancy, he responded to my emails right away, even after office hours.  He’s a fantastic doctor who I highly recommend.

originalText.text: Dr. Moritz was great--he saw us through our first pregnancy, answering all the millions of questions we had as nervous first-time parents-to-be in a knowledgeable and non-alarmist way.  I ended up having a cesarean due to the baby being breech, and the whole operation was very smooth and quick, as was the recovery.  He did much to put me at ease, which really helped.  The nurses and assistants he works with are also wonderful, as they were always really supportive and prompt about any questions or requests I had. Highly recommended!

originalText.text: Dr Moritz is one-of-a-kind.  I can honestly say that having him as an OB alleviated a lot of the stress that is to be expected during a high-risk pregnancy.  Each appointment was filled with equal parts of joyous levity and no nonsense straight-talk when needed.  Dr Moritz and his staff even accommodated us with a visit, between visits, to calm my nervous mom-to-be nerves.  He truly makes you feel like you are his most important patient.

originalText.text: I have been a patient of Dr. Moritz for over 15 years and I LOVE HIM!!!  He is funny and personable and makes an uncomfortable situation more bearable.   He helped me through a truly complicated pregnancy for both myself and my son to come out healthy and fine.  Hard to get an appointment because he is so great but he is definitely worth the wait.
